import { Grid, Link, Typography } from '@mui/material'

                <Typography variant='h6'>Contactanos</Typography>
                <Box sx={{display: "flex", flexDirection: "column"}}>

                    <Link href="#" underline="hover" color="#ff0">Sostenibilidad</Link>

            </Grid>

            <Grid item>

            </Grid>
        </Grid>

        <Box sx={{display: "flex", justifyContent: "center", marginTop: "1.25rem"}}>
            <Typography variant='subtitle2'>© 2022 Trippy LLC Todos los derechos reservados.</Typography>
